it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.routing

Class Route

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.routing.Route

  • public class Route
extends java.lang.Object
    An entry of a Routing Table. It is formed by a possible destination address or destination prefix, the address of the next-hop node, and the output interface.
